      <title>痛泻宁颗粒-一个中成药，既能调肝，又能调脾，肝好了，脾也好了</title>
      <link>https://qfmy321.github.io/post/zcy/tongxieningkeli/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Sep 2023 16:01:23 +0800</pubDate><author>me@example.com (ZY)</author>
